getObj

  • getObj(objId: string, ftype: BytesPlace, version: number, offset: number, maxLen: number): Promise<ObjReader>
    • Defined in 3nstorage/resources/store.ts:594

    Parameters

    • objId: string

      is a string object id for non-root objects, and null for root object.

    • ftype: BytesPlace
    • version: number

      is an integer version, or null, for current version.

    • offset: number

      is a read start point.

    • maxLen: number

      is a maximum number of bytes to read. Null indicates that all bytes can be read.

    Returns Promise<ObjReader>
